    "# 🏥 AI-Assisted Medical Report Analysis System\n",
    "## *For Rural Healthcare – AI-Based Health Advisory*\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "| Module | Technology |\n",
    "|--------|------------|\n",
    "| PDF Extraction | PyMuPDF (`fitz`) |\n",
    "| Image OCR | `pytesseract` + `EasyOCR` |\n",
