      "───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
      "  📄 PDF Processing Module — PyMuPDF\n",
      "───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
      "✅ Function ready: extract_text_from_pdf(pdf_path)\n",
      "\n",
      "Example usage:\n",
      "  import fitz\n",
      "  doc = fitz.open(\"report.pdf\")\n",
